section.section:
Of the 9 Board members:
5 shall be master heating, ventilation, air-conditioning, and refrigeration contractors licensed in the State, a subdivision of the State, or another state provided that state has licensing requirements equivalent to the licensing requirements of this title;
1 shall be a master electrician;
1 shall be a master plumber; and
2 shall be consumer members.

text.section:
Except for the initial members of the Board, of the members appointed under subsection (a)(2)(i), (ii), and (iii) of this section:
1 shall be from the area that consists of Caroline, Dorchester, Kent, Queen Anne's, Somerset, Talbot, Wicomico, and Worcester counties;
1 shall be from the area that consists of Baltimore City, and Baltimore, Cecil, and Harford counties;
1 shall be from the area that consists of Anne Arundel, Calvert, Charles, and St. Mary's counties;
1 shall be from the area that consists of Howard, Montgomery, and Prince George's counties; and
1 shall be from the area that consists of Allegany, Carroll, Frederick, Garrett, and Washington counties.
